# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:12
translate chinese whitneyp1_bf449e7e:

    # pc "Sorry if that's rude or anything. I know you're not supposed to ask a woman how old she is, but I was just wondering."
    pc "如果这显得失礼了，我很抱歉。我知道不该问女人的年龄，但我只是好奇。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:14
translate chinese whitneyp1_87660d67:

    # wt "Oh, I don't care about that. I'm 25."
    wt "哦，我不在乎那个。我25岁。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:15
translate chinese whitneyp1_2c1a5690:

    # pc "Just a few years older than me."
    pc "比我大几岁而已。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:16
translate chinese whitneyp1_6aa82862:

    # pc "I wasn't sure, because you look my age, but you sound and act like you're older. More mature."
    pc "我不确定，因为你看起来和我同龄，但说话和举止像个大姐姐。更成熟。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:18
translate chinese whitneyp1_a239d5d7:

    # wt "I grew up pretty fast, I guess."
    wt "我想我是早熟吧。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:19
translate chinese whitneyp1_2610fbfd:

    # wt "I've never paid too much attention to age."
    wt "我从来没太在意年龄。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:21
translate chinese whitneyp1_b6ed6f4b:

    # wt "Counting your time on Earth like it's a sort of accomplishment is a little strange, right?"
    wt "像数成就一样计算自己在世上的时间，有点奇怪，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:22
translate chinese whitneyp1_dbe0d848:

    # wt "Like, just being alive doesn't mean anything."
    wt "毕竟，仅仅活着并不代表什么。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:24
translate chinese whitneyp1_27ce3f09:

    # wt "I just want to accomplish things, and every year is one year less that I have time to do that."
    wt "我只想成就些事情，而每过一年，我用来实现这些目标的时间就少了一年。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:25
translate chinese whitneyp1_111a6060:

    # pc "Well, you're young. You have plenty of time."
    pc "嘛，你还年轻。时间多的是。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:27
translate chinese whitneyp1_0b182abd:

    # wt "I hope so. There is so much that i want to do."
    wt "希望如此。我还有那么多想做的事。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:28
translate chinese whitneyp1_3336e78d:

    # pc "I'm sure you will. Look at all the things that you've done already."
    pc "我相信你一定能做到。看看你已经做过的一切。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:30
translate chinese whitneyp1_05d9f799:

    # wt "Nothing that's going to help people, I don't think."
    wt "我觉得那些都没什么能帮助到别人的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:31
translate chinese whitneyp1_337cb7fb:

    # wt "But there's still time."
    wt "但时间还来得及。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:33
translate chinese whitneyp1_2bb0add7:

    # wt "And from now on, I'm only working on projects that I believe will make people's lives better."
    wt "从现在起，我只做那些我相信能让人们生活更美好的项目。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:34
translate chinese whitneyp1_612aa8d6:

    # pc "I'm glad you're on the side of good. A mind like yours could definitely do some harm if you were on the side of evil."
    pc "很高兴你站在了正义的一边。像你这样聪慧的头脑，若站在邪恶的一边，绝对会造成危害。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:36
translate chinese whitneyp1_54860455:

    # wt "I don't know about good and evil, but I understand what you're saying."
    wt "我不懂什么善恶，但我明白你的意思。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyp1.rpy:38
translate chinese whitneyp1_83cd531c:

    # wt "I'm only trying to help people now."
    wt "我现在只想帮助别人。"

